您可以通过查看点赞数量来了解您观看的视频有多有用。
它可以决定教育质量，尤其是在教育视频中。
从 2021 年 12 月 13 日开始，YouTube 从其 API 中删除了查看点赞的功能。使用 Show Youtube Dislike Counter YouDisLike 返回 YouTube 点赞。

您可以看到您想要的视频收到了多少个喜欢或不喜欢。
With Show Youtube Dislike Counter YouDisLike, the dislikes button comes back. 
You can understand how useful a video you watch is by looking at the number of dislikes. 
It can determine the quality of education, especially in educational videos.
Starting December 13th 2021, YouTube removed the ability to see dislikes from their API. With Show Youtube Dislike Counter YouDisLike return youtube dislike.

You can see how many likes or dislikes the video you want has received.

Shǐyòng Show Youtube Dislike Counter YouDisLike, diǎn zàn ànniǔ yòu huíláile.
Nín kěyǐ tōngguò chákàn diǎn zàn shùliàng lái liǎojiě nín guānkàn de shìpín yǒu duō yǒuyòng.
Tā kěyǐ juédìng jiàoyù zhìliàng, yóuqí shì zài jiàoyù shìpín zhōng.
Cóng 2021 nián 12 yuè 13 rì kāishǐ,YouTube cóng qí API zhōng shānchúle chákàn diǎn zàn de gōngnéng. Shǐyòng Show Youtube Dislike Counter YouDisLike fǎnhuí YouTube diǎn zàn.

Nín kěyǐ kàn dào nín xiǎng yào de shìpín shōu dàole duōshǎo gè xǐhuān huò bù xǐhuān.
